   <text>
      <body>
        <div type="letter">
            <opener><dateline><date when="1925-04-16">April 16, 1925</date></dateline><salute>My dear <persName key="richard_aldington">Mr. Aldington</persName>:</salute></opener>
            <p>You will be sorry to hear that <persName key="amy_lowell">Miss Lowell</persName> is seriously ill and has been obliged to give up the lecture trip to <placeName key="england">England</placeName> which she had intended to take this <date when="1925">Spring</date>. The doctors are keeping her very quiet in the hope of avoiding an operation which she is in no condition to stand.</p>
            <p>Of course she is bitterly disappointed, for this is the moment of moments for her to be in England.</p> 
            <closer>Yours very truly,
            <persName>Secretary</persName>.</closer> 
        </div>        
      </body>
